ğŸ’» How to Use

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/Bhaleraokunal/JAVA-CODE.git


Navigate to the folder of interest:

cd JAVA-CODE/Control_Flow_Statements


Open the .java file in your favorite IDE (Eclipse, IntelliJ, or VS Code) and run the program.

